name: WonderFi Technologies Inc.
longDescription: WonderFi Technologies Inc. owns, operates, incubates, and invests across the global digital asset ecosystem. It owns and operates two of Canada's most well-known and established crypto trading platforms Coinsquare and Bitbuy, as well as SmartPay, a global crypto payment processing platform. With a collective user base of over 1.6 million registered Canadians and a combined assets under custody exceeding $800 million, WonderFi boasts one of the largest communities of crypto investors within a single regulated ecosystem in Canada.
